with /* TPC-DS query24.tpl 0.92 */ ssales as
(select c_last_name
      ,c_first_name
      ,s_store_name
      ,ca_state
      ,s_state

    ,customer
    ,customer_address

      ,s_store_name
      ,sum(netpaid) paid
